}

### POST add new message with atachment
POST https://localhost/messages/add HTTP/1.1
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "groupId": "{{groupId}}",
    "threadId": "{{threadId}}",
    "attachment": {
        "mime": "image/png",
        "data": ""
        }
